| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1935 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 59a2a683-095e-5ec5-a264-d4cbc9754b6e"
